file.name: links_add.yml
file.content:
Add new bookmark for owner of current token
---
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
consumes:
  "application/json"
tags:
  - name: "Links"
parameters:
  - in: header
    name: Authorization
    description: "Send like this: Bearer [TOKEN]"
    type: string
    required: true
  - name: body
    in: body
    required: true
    schema:
      required:
        - url
      properties:
        url:
          type: string
          description: "Site Link"
          example: "https://stackoverflow.com"
        categories:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: "Categories which this site belongs to"
          example: ["programming", "developing", "search"]
        
responses:
  200:
    description: "Bookmark Added"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: int
          description: "Id of new added link"
      example:
        id: 12
  400:
    description: "Link is not valid"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: Link is not valid. Valid link looks like:http://example.com or https://example.com
      example:
        msg: Link is not valid. Valid link looks like:http://example.com or https://example.com
  500:
    description: "Failed to add new link"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: Failed to add new link
      example:
        msg: Failed to add new link
